**F001**

ID: F001  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: design-concern  
Type: behavior_change  
Before-behavior: 当前仓库里 [`ConceptGraphNode`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/models.py#L11>) 只承载图谱节点，`get_graph/get_mastery` 也是对整张图节点表直接聚合；设计文档把 BigConcept 定义为导航容器，不是图上的节点。  
After-behavior: 计划把 BigConcept 也写进 `concept_graph_nodes`，再依赖 `node_type='concept'` 过滤把它们从 graph/mastery/search 中排除。  
Evidence: [`plan.md#L7`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L7>)、[`plan.md#L132`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L132>)、[`plan.md#L211`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L211>)、[`plan.md#L269`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L269>) 明确要求同步/存储 `big_concept` 节点；但 [`design.md#L58`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L58>)、[`design.md#L59`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L59>) 规定 BigConcept 不是图节点。  
Impact: 这会把“导航容器”和“图谱主节点”混进同一投影表，直接放大到 sync、service、router、search、mastery、前端树和详情等多个风险模块，违背 [`architecture-rules.md#L37`](</C:/Users/Administrator/.claude/rules-t3/architecture-rules.md#L37>)、[`architecture-rules.md#L58`](</C:/Users/Administrator/.claude/rules-t3/architecture-rules.md#L58>) 的接口隔离和影响面控制要求；任何遗漏一个过滤点，都会把 BigConcept 泄漏到掌握度、搜索结果或编辑路径。  
Repair hypothesis:  
1. likely repair direction: 先把“导航持久化契约”和“图谱节点投影契约”重新拆清，再决定 BigConcept 是否需要独立投影而不是混入 `concept_graph_nodes`。  
2. forbidden fix patterns to avoid: 继续在各端点/组件散落补 `node_type != 'big_concept'`；把存储层补丁暴露成 API 契约。  
3. requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

