**F002**

ID: F002  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: 设计要求迁移脚本按 `curriculum_requirements.big_concept + module` 聚合 BigConcept，并从 L1 JSON 迁移 `aliases_json`/`evidence_ids_json`，下游详情和搜索依赖这些字段。  
After-behavior: 计划把 BigConcept 成功标准硬编码成 `11`，且 Task 1 的核心步骤没有把 `aliases_json`/`evidence_ids_json` 作为独立迁移契约；但 Task 5 又假定 `evidence_ids_json` 已存在并可读。  
Evidence: [`plan.md#L36`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L36>)、[`plan.md#L57`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L57>)、[`plan.md#L84`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L84>) 把验收数写成 11；[`plan.md#L71`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L71>) 到 [`plan.md#L76`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L76>) 未覆盖 alias/evidence 迁移；但 [`plan.md#L360`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L360>)、[`plan.md#L388`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L388>) 又依赖 `evidence_ids_json`。对应设计是 [`design.md#L104`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L104>)、[`design.md#L139`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L139>)、[`design.md#L301`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L301>)、[`design.md#L310`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L310>)。  
Impact: 迁移脚本可能在错误聚合下仍“通过”，并把跨模块 BigConcept 错合并；同时详情页的 Evidence 和搜索别名能力缺少数据回填保障，属于先天性脏数据入口。  
Repair hypothesis: 把 Task 1 的验收标准改成“基于源数据推导的 module-scoped 实际基线”，并把 `aliases_json`、`evidence_ids_json` 回填各自升级为独立测试契约，而不是依赖后续 Task 间接发现。

