**F003**

ID: F003  
Severity: HIGH  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: 设计定义了审核状态机 `ai_draft -> teacher_reviewed -> published`，并要求 `reviewed_by/reviewed_at` 可追溯，且“已发布概念被修改时自动回退到 `ai_draft`”。  
After-behavior: 计划只新增 `review_status` 字段和 `set_review_status` 直接写库，`update_node` 还允许直接更新 `review_status`，没有审计字段、没有来源字段，也没有“发布后修改自动回退”的契约。  
Evidence: 设计要求见 [`design.md#L72`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L72>)、[`design.md#L117`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L117>)、[`design.md#L151`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L151>)、[`design.md#L261`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L261>)；计划实现只覆盖 [`plan.md#L131`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L131>) 到 [`plan.md#L137`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L137>)、[`plan.md#L441`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L441>)、[`plan.md#L470`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L470>)、[`plan.md#L476`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L476>)。  
Impact: 审核流会退化成普通字段写入，既无法追溯“谁在何时批准”，也无法防止 published 内容被直接修改后仍保持 published；这属于典型 state machine 红旗。  
Repair hypothesis:  
1. likely repair direction: 先补完整审核状态契约，明确可迁移的状态、修改触发的状态回退、以及审计字段的真源。  
2. forbidden fix patterns to avoid: 仅靠 UI 按钮限制状态；继续把 `review_status` 放入普通白名单字段；事后补 timestamp/user 而不定义转移规则。  
3. requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

