ID: F005  
Severity: MED  
Category: code-bug  
Type: defect_fix  
Before-behavior: 现有 `router.py` 是薄路由，查询逻辑委托给 service；设计里的搜索契约要求匹配 `canonical_name + aliases_json + description`。  
After-behavior: 计划把 SQLAlchemy 查询直接塞进 `router.py`，且只搜 `name + aliases_json`，把 `description` 从设计契约里丢掉。  
Evidence: 现状见 [`router.py#L20`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py#L20>)、[`router.py#L63`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/router.py#L63>)；计划代码见 [`plan.md#L393`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L393>) 到 [`plan.md#L416`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-plan.md#L416>)；设计要求在 [`design.md#L247`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L247>) 到 [`design.md#L253`](</C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-09-knowledge-graph-restructure-design.md#L253>)；架构规则禁止“路由文件里混入业务逻辑和数据库查询”，见 [`architecture-rules.md#L23`](</C:/Users/Administrator/.claude/rules-t3/architecture-rules.md#L23>)、[`architecture-rules.md#L27`](</C:/Users/Administrator/.claude/rules-t3/architecture-rules.md#L27>)。  
Impact: 搜索能力会漏掉仅出现在描述里的概念，同时把数据库字段和鉴权/查询细节耦合进路由层，后续任何搜索扩展都会额外拉大变更面。  
Repair hypothesis:  
1. likely repair direction: 把搜索收敛成 service 层契约，并先定清搜索字段、返回结构、权限与排序规则。  
2. forbidden fix patterns to avoid: 在 router 内继续堆查询分支；前端依赖 `aliases_json`/`primary_module` 这类存储字段名作为稳定接口。  
3. requires independent fix design + Semantic Regression Gate

